{
  "spec": {
    "title": "Media Capture from DOM Elements",
    "url": "https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-fromelement/"
  },
  "algorithms": [
    {
      "html": "A new frame is requested from the canvas when\n                <a data-xref-type=\"attribute\" data-link-type=\"attribute\" data-link-for=\"track\" data-xref-for=\"track\" data-lt=\"[[frameCaptureRequested]]\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-fromelement/#dfn-framecapturerequested\" class=\"internalDFN\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-framecapturerequested-3\"><code>[[frameCaptureRequested]]</code></a> is true and the canvas is painted. Each\n                time that the captured canvas is painted, the following steps are executed:",
      "rationale": "for",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "For each <var>track</var> capturing from the canvas execute the following\n                steps:",
          "rationale": "if",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "If new content has been drawn to the canvas since it was last painted, and\n                    if the <a data-xref-type=\"attribute\" data-link-type=\"attribute\" data-link-for=\"track\" data-xref-for=\"track\" data-lt=\"[[frameCaptureRequested]]\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-fromelement/#dfn-framecapturerequested\" class=\"internalDFN\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-framecapturerequested-4\"><code>[[frameCaptureRequested]]</code></a> internal slot of\n                    <var>track</var> is set, add a new frame to <var>track</var> containing what\n                    was painted to the canvas."
            },
            {
              "html": "If a <var>frameRequestRate</var> value was specified, set the\n                    <a data-xref-type=\"attribute\" data-link-type=\"attribute\" data-link-for=\"track\" data-xref-for=\"track\" data-lt=\"[[frameCaptureRequested]]\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-fromelement/#dfn-framecapturerequested\" class=\"internalDFN\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-framecapturerequested-5\"><code>[[frameCaptureRequested]]</code></a> internal slot of <var>track</var>\n                    to <code>false</code>."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}